status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
i.e.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{supp}(q(x_{t}|x_{t-1},y_{t}))\supset\mathrm{supp}(p(x_{t}|y_{1:t}))$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset

